      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 4,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 4,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "React 19 + Vite 6\nTailwind v4 + shadcn\n\nZod:\n• env (VITE_*)\n• auth forms (login/register)\n• product filters (URL)\n• chat message + response\n• api-error parser\n\nTanStack Query (catálogo)\nZustand (auth persist)\nFramer Motion (cards)\n\nSocket.IO client → /events\n(pedidos em tempo real)\n\nREST → API + IA",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "React 19 + Vite 6\nTailwind v4 + shadcn\n\nZod:\n• env (VITE_*)\n• auth forms (login/register)\n• product filters (URL)\n• chat message + response\n• api-error parser\n\nTanStack Query (catálogo)\nZustand (auth persist)\nFramer Motion (cards)\n\nSocket.IO client → /events\n(pedidos em tempo real)\n\nREST → API + IA",
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
